text: The traditional horse statues ride. Not that fun for children now. (But they were, when I was young!). Playground suitable for 3-5 year olds.

There is a decent small playground with Two Swings and a huge covered foyer for gatherings and indoor resident activities. Unfortunately it could have been further utilized with a bigger playground space for the children.Maybe more swings,a slide or even a merry go round which is absent in modern heartland playgrounds.I see many kids waiting and mostly don't even stood a chance at getting a decent feeling on the much awaited swing.

Many different playground items for kids to have fun. Swings, slides, 'monuments', etc..

Bring mosquito repellent as per all playground given the proximity to drains and greeneries
A nice location to unwind. It features a variety of playground equipment that children will enjoy.
Nostalgic old singapore in its oldest form
